description:
Unladen Swallow: fewer coconuts, faster Python

Collin Winter (Google / Unladen Swallow)

Unladen Swallow is a Google-sponsored optimization branch of CPython.
This talk will cover Google's motivation for Unladen Swallow, the
approach being taken, results so far, challenges faced, cancers cured
and plans for merger with CPython.
title: Unladen Swallow: fewer coconuts, faster Python (#73)
